KCCAns: RECOMMENDED FOR SPRAY AZADIRACHTIN 1% NEEM EXTRACT CONCENTRATE @3ML PER LITRE OF WATER

QueryText: Asking about preparation of field in cauliflower
KCCAns: Recommended for Bring the soil to fine tilth and pits should be taken at a spacing of 45 cm either way in hills. Form ridges and furrows at 60 cm in plains
